Most Midgaard residents have never met a Rivennid. The connection between the city's sealed warrants and the Rivennid's existence is not part of any civic curriculum.
The arcanist registry contains "anomalous decay pattern" reports from northern forest scouts — filed without action by both factions for different reasons.
The Reckoning faction knows Rivennid institutional analysis provides the most comprehensive evidentiary account of what the sealed warrants actually produced.
The Continuity faction treats the Withered Depths as a geographic hazard rather than an institutional consequence.
Rivennid who travel to Midgaard — uncommon — carry forest corruption assessments that they provide to Reckoning scholars in exchange for institutional movement on sealed warrant disclosure.

